text: Bosminidae is a family of anomopods in the order Diplostraca. There are at least 3 genera and 40 described species in Bosminidae. ==Genera== * Bosmina Baird, 1845 * Bosminopsis Richard, 1895 * Eubosmina Seligo, 1900 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * Category:Cladocera
title: Bosminidae
